                        <r3d:remarks>RESIF is a consortium of French research bodies and academic establishments. Coordinated by the CNRS-INSU, this network relies on the Observatoires des Sciences de l’Univers which are present throughout the whole of France. It is composed of seismographs (velocity meters and accelerometers), geodetic instruments (GNSS) and gravimeters. Read more https://www.resif.fr/presentation/organisation/?article65</r3d:remarks>
